        <trans-unit id="103" translate="yes" xml:space="preserve">
          <source>In the Microsoft Foundation Class Library (MFC), class <bpt id="p1">[</bpt>CFile<ept id="p1">](../mfc/reference/cfile-class.md)</ept> handles normal file I/O operations.</source>
        </trans-unit>
